@madonna covered @interviewmag again and I’m sick in the best way. For the Summer 2026 issue, the icon returns for her 10th cover, the most in the publication’s history.
Shot by @nadialeecohen and styled by @melzy917, the story introduces “Dee Dee”—a larger-than-life alter ego with big hair, bigger attitude, and a taste for chaos. It’s cinematic, self-aware, and exactly the kind of character study Madonna has built a career on.
#Madonna #InterviewMagazine #FashionEditorial #PopCulture

